msgid "Manage the local IPTV playlist refresh service. The API token remains on the router and is never sent to this browser."
msgstr "管理本地 IPTV 播放列表刷新服务。API 令牌保留在路由器上，绝不会发送到此浏览器。"

msgid "Multicast endpoint"
msgstr "组播端点"

msgid "Must match the R2H Token configured in luci-app-rtp2httpd."
msgstr "必须与 luci-app-rtp2httpd 中配置的 R2H Token 一致。"

